WEBVTT

00:01.835 --> 00:04.771
[cheerful music]

00:04.838 --> 00:12.746
♪ ♪

00:12.812 --> 00:14.547
♪ Harvey ♪

00:14.614 --> 00:16.649
♪ ♪

00:16.716 --> 00:18.785
♪ Harvey ♪

00:18.852 --> 00:24.758
♪ ♪

00:24.824 --> 00:27.093
♪ Harvey ♪

00:27.160 --> 00:28.995
♪ ♪

00:31.998 --> 00:35.435
♪ Love me to me,
love me to you ♪

00:35.502 --> 00:36.436
♪ You do... ♪

00:36.503 --> 00:39.439
{\an1}(Foo)
Hey, Claire.

00:39.506 --> 00:41.307
♪ Beach and the sand ♪

00:41.374 --> 00:42.308
Oh.

00:42.375 --> 00:43.343
Hi, Foo.

00:43.410 --> 00:45.645
{\an3}Do you want to go
for a ride?

00:45.712 --> 00:47.914
{\an1}[snoring]

00:47.981 --> 00:48.681
♪ We never split ♪

00:48.748 --> 00:51.418
♪ I hashtag commit ♪

00:51.484 --> 00:52.852
[crunching, slurping]

00:52.919 --> 00:54.621
Are you gonna eat that?

00:54.687 --> 00:55.221
Yeah--oh.

00:55.288 --> 00:58.091
Never mind.

00:58.158 --> 01:00.693
[chewing, sputtering]

01:00.760 --> 01:02.896
{\an3}Claire, I have something
to ask you.

01:02.962 --> 01:04.531
Y-yes, Foo?

01:04.596 --> 01:06.299
Will you be my...

01:06.366 --> 01:09.235
girlfriend?

01:09.302 --> 01:11.204
Ah!

01:11.271 --> 01:13.673
Oh, Foo, of course I will.

01:13.740 --> 01:15.341
[sighs]

01:15.408 --> 01:19.045
♪ Love me to me,
love me to you ♪

01:19.112 --> 01:22.549
♪ You do me love to you ♪

01:22.615 --> 01:25.351
♪ Love me to me, to me ♪

01:25.418 --> 01:27.120
[sighs]

01:27.187 --> 01:28.621
- Claire!
- Ah!

01:28.688 --> 01:29.722
Piri, where are we going?

01:29.789 --> 01:32.358
{\an3}Welcome to
the secret circle.

01:32.425 --> 01:34.461
Hi.

01:34.527 --> 01:36.596
{\an6}(Piri Piri)
Whatever is revealed
in the circle

01:36.663 --> 01:37.330
stays in the circle.

01:37.397 --> 01:40.400
You may enter.

01:40.467 --> 01:41.367
Zhoov!

01:41.434 --> 01:43.336
Zshh!

01:43.403 --> 01:45.505
Okay, the circle is now closed.

01:45.572 --> 01:47.941
Time is moving so fast,

01:48.007 --> 01:50.410
and we are all growing
into incredible women.

01:50.477 --> 01:51.411
I'm not a girl.

01:51.478 --> 01:54.481
{\an3}Let's all share
our deepest secrets.

01:54.547 --> 01:55.381
I'll go first.

01:55.448 --> 01:58.751
My secret is,
sometimes I...

01:58.818 --> 02:01.387
I don't really like
cinnamon buns.

02:01.454 --> 02:02.455
Kratz, your turn.

02:02.522 --> 02:04.524
Well, I think
I'm growing an extra toe.

02:04.591 --> 02:07.126
Lame!
My turn!

02:07.193 --> 02:10.029
The truth is,
I'm good at everything,

02:10.096 --> 02:12.732
and I don't even try.

02:12.799 --> 02:13.800
My secret's the best!

02:13.867 --> 02:14.801
I win!

02:14.868 --> 02:16.135
Claire, what about you?

02:16.202 --> 02:18.037
Oh, uh, I don't know.

02:18.104 --> 02:19.739
It's--it's dumb.

02:19.806 --> 02:20.740
You're in a safe place.

02:20.807 --> 02:25.512
Um, okay, well,
my secret is...

02:25.578 --> 02:27.680
I have a crush on Foo.

02:27.747 --> 02:29.616
- [gasps]
- That's beautiful.

02:29.682 --> 02:30.817
You have to tell him.

02:30.884 --> 02:32.118
What?

02:32.185 --> 02:34.220
I thought our secrets
stayed in the circle.

02:34.287 --> 02:36.623
But, Claire, this is amazing.

02:36.689 --> 02:38.491
You have to shout this
from the mountains.

02:38.558 --> 02:41.094
There are some feelings
you have to bottle up forever.

02:41.160 --> 02:42.929
You can't just
blurt everything out.

02:42.996 --> 02:44.297
[Fee belches]

02:44.364 --> 02:46.332
{\an3}[sighs]

02:46.399 --> 02:47.534
{\an3}Hey, dudes.

02:47.600 --> 02:50.003
I wanted to see
what life was like as a ball.

02:50.069 --> 02:53.239
{\an3}Foo, Claire has something
she wants to tell you.

02:53.306 --> 02:54.407
{\an1}What?

02:54.474 --> 02:55.208
No, I don't.

02:55.275 --> 02:56.576
{\an1}Go ahead.
It'll be fine.

02:56.643 --> 02:57.610
No, I don't want to.

02:57.677 --> 02:58.611
Ah!

02:58.678 --> 02:59.746
[grunting]

02:59.812 --> 03:01.447
{\an3}Rah!
Give it!

03:01.514 --> 03:02.181
{\an1}Hey!

03:02.248 --> 03:03.349
Foo is my boyfriend now.

03:03.416 --> 03:05.451
{\an3}Oh, okay.

03:05.518 --> 03:06.753
[gasps]

03:06.819 --> 03:08.655
[dramatic music]

03:08.721 --> 03:10.957
Why would she do that
after I just said--

03:11.024 --> 03:12.292
What the heck?

03:12.358 --> 03:14.394
Princess thinks she can
just steal my brother?

03:14.460 --> 03:17.163
{\an3}Nuh-uh, I am breaking them up
right now.

03:17.230 --> 03:17.931
I want to help.

03:17.997 --> 03:18.998
No offense, Claire,

03:19.065 --> 03:20.700
but you'd just
slow me down.

03:20.767 --> 03:22.835
Have you ever even swung a mace?

03:22.902 --> 03:25.004
I don't--what's a mace?

03:25.071 --> 03:26.973
Is that like a hair clip?

03:27.040 --> 03:29.208
{\an3}Claire, Claire,
stop talking.

03:29.275 --> 03:30.209
I'm gonna go now.

03:30.276 --> 03:31.978
Wait, I want to come too.

03:32.045 --> 03:33.146
I'll swing a mace.

03:33.212 --> 03:34.347
I'll take a life.

03:34.414 --> 03:36.082
I'll do whatever it takes!

03:36.149 --> 03:38.017
{\an3}Um, okay.

03:38.084 --> 03:39.552
You can carry my stuff.

03:39.619 --> 03:43.056
Then I'll have a chance
to win Foo for myself.

03:43.122 --> 03:45.858
[romantic music]

03:45.925 --> 03:46.960
What are you doing?

03:47.026 --> 03:48.094
{\an1}Nothing.

03:48.461 --> 03:50.096
Gotcha!

03:50.163 --> 03:50.697
Ooh, hey!

03:50.763 --> 03:53.066
{\an3}[laughing]

03:53.132 --> 03:55.101
Catch the laser.

03:55.168 --> 03:56.769
Okay, Foo, entertain me.

03:56.836 --> 03:58.838
Do an impression of something.

03:58.905 --> 04:00.473
Okay.

04:00.540 --> 04:02.275
Ta-da!

04:02.342 --> 04:04.911
Mm-kay, now tell me
something sweet.

04:04.978 --> 04:06.946
My head is full of blood.

04:07.013 --> 04:07.880
[laughing]

04:07.947 --> 04:11.150
{\an3}Ugh,
she's got to be stopped.

04:11.217 --> 04:12.118
Here's my plan.

04:12.185 --> 04:14.921
I have a mace.

04:14.988 --> 04:16.755
Okay, and then what?

04:16.822 --> 04:19.058
Um, I just said,
"I have a mace."

04:19.125 --> 04:21.027
How about I create
a distraction,

04:21.094 --> 04:22.762
and then you go rescue Foo?

04:22.829 --> 04:24.430
Hmm, go on.

04:24.497 --> 04:26.032
Princess loves
shiny things,

04:26.099 --> 04:27.533
so I'll get her attention

04:27.600 --> 04:29.736
{\an3}with these trophies that
my sister won.

04:29.802 --> 04:31.070
I stole them.

04:31.137 --> 04:32.105
Don't tell her.

04:32.171 --> 04:33.339
I'm impressed.

04:33.406 --> 04:34.807
You're braver than I thought.

04:34.874 --> 04:35.875
R-really?

04:35.942 --> 04:37.043
Thanks.

04:37.110 --> 04:39.145
Okay, now do some somersaults.

04:39.212 --> 04:41.047
Ow!
What the heck?

04:41.114 --> 04:42.849
Shiny.

04:42.915 --> 04:44.050
Okay, Fee.

04:44.117 --> 04:46.085
The owl is in flight.

04:46.152 --> 04:47.754
Shiny, shiny, shiny!

04:47.820 --> 04:50.356
Foo, I'm rescuing you,

04:50.423 --> 04:52.492
{\an3}and I look really cool
right now.

04:52.558 --> 04:53.893
[grunting]

04:53.960 --> 04:54.861
Ah!

04:54.927 --> 04:56.162
[laughing]

04:56.229 --> 04:58.131
Okay, Foo, let's go.

04:58.197 --> 04:59.332
[whistles]

04:59.399 --> 05:00.133
Oh.

05:00.199 --> 05:01.134
{\an3}[chuckling]

05:01.200 --> 05:03.770
{\an1}Rats, she's gotten
into his head.

05:03.836 --> 05:05.071
Nice mace work, though.

05:05.138 --> 05:06.072
{\an3}Thanks.

05:06.139 --> 05:07.507
I trained myself.

05:07.573 --> 05:09.475
(Princess)
[grunting] Come on, Foo.

05:09.542 --> 05:10.443
Hold still.

05:10.510 --> 05:11.210
If you're gonna be
seen with me,

05:11.277 --> 05:13.246
you have to up your game.

05:13.312 --> 05:14.781
Right now you're a two,

05:14.847 --> 05:18.184
but I will make you a ten.

05:18.251 --> 05:22.021
I got to go get
all my dad's expensive lotions.

05:22.088 --> 05:24.057
Princess' house
is so easy to break into.

05:24.123 --> 05:27.593
{\an3}Okay, what if we made Foo
really ugly?

05:27.660 --> 05:29.228
{\an3}Princess would
totally dump him.

05:29.295 --> 05:31.831
{\an1}Making Foo ugly
will be pretty hard.

05:31.898 --> 05:33.399
But I have this.

05:33.466 --> 05:35.735
I tried to make
spaghetti sauce once,

05:35.802 --> 05:37.804
but it turned out...evil.

05:37.870 --> 05:38.738
{\an3}Perfect.

05:38.805 --> 05:40.940
Heh-heh, you're a genius.

05:41.007 --> 05:44.744
[mischievous music]

05:44.811 --> 05:45.478
{\an3}(Princess)
Hold still.

05:45.545 --> 05:47.113
I'm making you pretty.

05:47.180 --> 05:48.247
I'll dump the whole jar.

05:48.314 --> 05:50.650
I don't even care.

05:50.717 --> 05:52.819
[sizzling]

05:52.885 --> 05:54.220
Oh.

05:54.287 --> 05:56.556
My hands look
like Harvey's feet.

05:56.622 --> 05:58.124
Ew, ew, ew!

05:58.191 --> 06:00.093
Am I a ten yet?

06:00.159 --> 06:01.194
Ah!

06:01.260 --> 06:02.662
[both snickering]

06:02.729 --> 06:05.064
I can't be seen with you
like this.

06:05.131 --> 06:06.065
{\an3}(Princess)
Ugh!

06:06.132 --> 06:07.867
This is a "make it work" moment.

06:07.934 --> 06:09.302
[laughter]

06:12.572 --> 06:14.707
[buzzing]

06:14.774 --> 06:15.975
♪ La la la la ♪

06:16.042 --> 06:18.478
Ah, look,
she's coming.

06:18.544 --> 06:19.912
Quick, give me your glasses.

06:19.979 --> 06:21.981
[giggles]

06:22.048 --> 06:22.682
Ah, that sign!

06:22.749 --> 06:25.218
Froyo and attention?

06:25.284 --> 06:26.886
[hyperventilating]

06:26.953 --> 06:28.087
Give me all of it!

06:28.154 --> 06:30.223
(both)
Welcome!

06:30.289 --> 06:32.258
Put froyo in my mouth now.

06:32.325 --> 06:33.760
Right away, ma'am.

06:33.826 --> 06:34.961
{\an3}By the way,

06:35.027 --> 06:35.561
{\an3}is that your grandma
over there?

06:35.628 --> 06:38.231
[grunting]

06:38.297 --> 06:39.165
{\an3}What? No!

06:39.232 --> 06:40.466
That's my boyfriend.

06:40.533 --> 06:43.703
{\an3}Your boyfriend
doesn't get you froyo?

06:43.770 --> 06:44.604
{\an3}That's sad.

06:44.670 --> 06:46.939
If I were you,
I'd dump him.

06:47.006 --> 06:48.274
What? No!

06:48.341 --> 06:48.808
My boyfriend's the best!

06:48.875 --> 06:50.643
Oh, yeah?

06:50.710 --> 06:52.745
Well, my boyfriend
flies me everywhere.

06:52.812 --> 06:55.314
Well, my boyfriend

06:55.381 --> 06:57.150
gets me presents
made of lasers.

06:57.216 --> 06:58.384
Pyoo!
Pyoo-pyoo-pyoo!

06:58.451 --> 07:02.889
Well, my boyfriend
has sugar and candy and...

07:02.955 --> 07:07.026
Yeah, well, my boyfriend
has all the money in the world.

07:07.093 --> 07:08.127
Oh, yeah?
Well...

07:08.194 --> 07:09.762
{\an3}(Claire)
And he loves me, and...

07:09.829 --> 07:11.164
Well, my boyfriend--

07:11.230 --> 07:12.899
{\an1}[screams]

07:12.965 --> 07:13.966
I dug a hole.

07:14.033 --> 07:15.501
{\an3}You have
to treat me better,

07:15.568 --> 07:16.469
{\an3}and you have to learn
how to fly.

07:16.536 --> 07:19.005
- Okay.
- I'm glad we made up.

07:20.339 --> 07:21.440
{\an3}[laughs]

07:21.507 --> 07:23.609
{\an3}Oh, man,
it didn't work.

07:23.676 --> 07:24.844
[laughter]

07:24.911 --> 07:27.013
I think we got
under her skin this time.

07:27.079 --> 07:29.081
Yeah, we make a good team.

07:29.148 --> 07:30.516
{\an1}You're pretty cool,
Claire.

07:30.583 --> 07:32.318
When we get Foo back,
the three of us should

07:32.385 --> 07:33.519
{\an1}throw water balloons
at people or something.

07:33.586 --> 07:37.123
Actually, Fee,
I have something to tell you.

07:37.190 --> 07:38.191
Sure.

07:38.257 --> 07:39.458
Spill those beans.

07:40.860 --> 07:43.162
{\an3}Whoo.

07:43.229 --> 07:46.199
{\an3}Okay, the secret circle
has been formed.

07:46.265 --> 07:48.134
The truth is...

07:48.201 --> 07:49.769
I have a crush on Foo.

07:49.836 --> 07:53.606
[romantic music]

07:53.673 --> 07:54.774
Um, what?

07:54.841 --> 07:57.143
I like Foo?

07:57.210 --> 08:00.079
{\an1}I thought
you were my friend,

08:00.146 --> 08:01.681
but you're just like Princess.

08:01.747 --> 08:03.883
{\an1}You just want to get
between me and my brother.

08:03.950 --> 08:05.184
W-what?

08:05.251 --> 08:07.553
I'll just have
to rescue Foo by myself.

08:07.620 --> 08:08.988
{\an3}Wait.

08:09.055 --> 08:09.989
You know what?

08:10.056 --> 08:11.991
I hate secret circles.

08:12.058 --> 08:14.493
[Foo humming cheerfully]

08:14.560 --> 08:16.162
I drew a foot with eyes,

08:16.229 --> 08:17.964
and it's holding
a ninja star.

08:18.030 --> 08:19.365
Ugh, quit being weird.

08:19.432 --> 08:20.299
You're running out of space.

08:20.366 --> 08:23.469
{\an1}Just draw a heart
with our names.

08:23.536 --> 08:24.937
I don't need Claire

08:25.004 --> 08:27.139
{\an1}or her strategies
or plans.

08:27.206 --> 08:29.175
{\an1}I just need Foo,
and that's it.

08:29.242 --> 08:31.744
{\an1}Princess,
you let my brother go,

08:31.811 --> 08:32.345
{\an1}or else.

08:32.410 --> 08:34.614
Or else what?

08:37.884 --> 08:39.751
[inhaling]

08:39.818 --> 08:42.355
[high-pitched]
You think you can take me alone?

08:42.421 --> 08:43.022
[battle cry]

08:43.089 --> 08:45.324
[heavy thuds]

08:45.391 --> 08:47.260
[both grunting]

08:47.326 --> 08:48.327
Okay, when I see Fee,

08:48.394 --> 08:50.930
I'm gonna say,
"I'm sorry."

08:50.997 --> 08:51.631
[thud]

08:51.697 --> 08:52.498
"I didn't mean to"--

08:52.565 --> 08:55.001
- Oh, my gosh.
[both grunt]

08:55.067 --> 08:55.968
Oh, no.

08:56.035 --> 08:57.003
Fee needs my help.

08:57.069 --> 08:58.004
I-I have to do something.

08:58.070 --> 09:00.139
I'm gonna spit on you.

09:00.206 --> 09:01.974
Not if I spit on you first.

09:02.041 --> 09:02.909
[spitting]

09:02.975 --> 09:04.577
Oh, hi, guys.

09:04.644 --> 09:09.348
I'm just having a romantic walk
with my new boyfriend.

09:09.415 --> 09:12.351
{\an3}His name is Vance.
He's a DJ.

09:12.418 --> 09:13.519
{\an1}Ew, what?

09:13.586 --> 09:15.321
{\an3}If someone
stole him from me,

09:15.388 --> 09:18.324
I'd be so jealous.

09:18.391 --> 09:21.794
{\an3}Right, Fee?

09:21.861 --> 09:23.362
Um, yeah.

09:23.429 --> 09:23.829
Everyone wants him.

09:23.896 --> 09:25.765
{\an1}What?

09:25.831 --> 09:26.966
Hey, step off.

09:27.033 --> 09:28.935
{\an3}I want him to be
my BF.

09:29.001 --> 09:29.702
You can't have him.

09:29.769 --> 09:31.771
I can't live without him.

09:31.837 --> 09:33.005
[laughter]

09:33.072 --> 09:34.040
{\an3}Hey!

09:34.106 --> 09:35.408
My boyfriend is better!

09:35.474 --> 09:36.676
{\an3}You guys should
be fighting over him!

09:36.742 --> 09:38.477
{\an1}[scoffs]

09:38.544 --> 09:40.579
{\an1}Everyone has a crush
on Vance now.

09:40.646 --> 09:44.016
{\an3}Yeah, if you don't have Vance,
then you aren't the best.

09:44.083 --> 09:45.151
[growling]

09:45.217 --> 09:48.054
{\an3}Foo, hey,
I'm dumping you.

09:48.120 --> 09:49.255
Okay.

09:49.322 --> 09:51.557
{\an1}Vance, I've waited
my whole life for you.

09:51.624 --> 09:53.059
You complete me!

09:53.125 --> 09:53.926
You're all jealous.

09:53.993 --> 09:57.029
{\an3}[laughing]

09:57.096 --> 09:58.764
What a dum-dum.

09:58.831 --> 10:00.933
{\an3}Um, Fee,
I'm sorry about before.

10:01.000 --> 10:01.767
Please don't hate me.

10:01.834 --> 10:04.470
{\an1}[sighs]
Maybe I overreacted.

10:04.537 --> 10:07.106
{\an1}I just don't want
to see Foo get hurt.

10:07.173 --> 10:09.175
Ooh, I'm falling.

10:09.241 --> 10:10.977
Let's just forget
about my crush.

10:11.043 --> 10:12.345
{\an1}What?
No way.

10:12.411 --> 10:13.913
{\an1}Claire, listen,
I think you're cool.

10:13.980 --> 10:15.948
And Foo is cool.

10:16.015 --> 10:18.184
So if you two
want to be cool together,

10:18.250 --> 10:19.652
then you have my blessing.

10:19.719 --> 10:21.620
- Alley-oop.
- Ah!

10:21.687 --> 10:22.488
{\an3}Oof.

10:24.890 --> 10:25.958
{\an3}Hey, Foo.

10:26.025 --> 10:27.793
Oh, hey, Claire.

10:27.860 --> 10:30.162
I have something to tell you.

10:30.229 --> 10:32.331
Oh, okay.

10:32.398 --> 10:35.668
Foo, uh, I like you.

10:35.735 --> 10:37.937
Claire, I like you too.

10:38.004 --> 10:38.971
Really?

10:39.038 --> 10:42.341
{\an1}Yep, and I like this rock
and this leaf,

10:42.408 --> 10:44.844
and I like squishing my mouth
all tiny.

10:44.910 --> 10:48.214
But, um, do you like me
in a girlfriend way?

10:48.280 --> 10:48.781
Girlfriend...

10:48.848 --> 10:50.549
sure.

10:50.616 --> 10:52.118
And this is my rock-friend,

10:52.184 --> 10:53.519
and this is my leaf-friend.

10:53.586 --> 10:55.421
{\an1}This is a fun game.
[grunts]

10:55.488 --> 10:57.289
[Foo laughing]

10:57.356 --> 10:58.624
Sorry, Claire.

10:58.691 --> 11:00.893
{\an3}I don't think Foo
is ready to be a boyfriend.

11:00.960 --> 11:02.061
Eh, that's okay.

11:02.128 --> 11:03.329
I may not have a boyfriend,

11:03.396 --> 11:05.498
{\an1}but at least
I have a Fee-friend.

11:05.564 --> 11:07.099
{\an3}[belches]

11:07.166 --> 11:09.001
{\an3}That was
my celebration burp.

11:09.068 --> 11:10.569
Oh, okay, here's mine.

11:10.636 --> 11:11.537
[belches quietly]

11:11.604 --> 11:13.539
I feel alive!

11:13.606 --> 11:15.541
[laughter]

11:17.043 --> 11:19.812
[laughter]

11:26.952 --> 11:29.388
Don't splash me so much.

11:29.455 --> 11:31.090
[ominous music]

11:31.157 --> 11:32.458
Whoa.

11:32.525 --> 11:33.659
{\an3}Hey, Kratz.

11:33.726 --> 11:35.528
How come you ain't swimming,
buddy?

11:35.594 --> 11:37.129
Harvey, look.

11:37.196 --> 11:40.332
{\an3}There's a scary face
in the clouds.

11:40.399 --> 11:42.334
{\an1}(Harvey)
Hmm.

11:42.401 --> 11:44.270
Kratz, I don't see--

11:44.336 --> 11:47.840
Oh, wait a second.

11:47.907 --> 11:48.574
I do see something.

11:48.641 --> 11:50.476
Yeah, Kratz, I see it.

11:50.543 --> 11:53.612
Yeah, it's a horsey head!

11:53.679 --> 11:56.682
(Kratz)
No, it's a scary face,

11:56.749 --> 11:58.851
and I'm pretty sure
he's laughing at me.

11:58.918 --> 12:00.152
[echoing laughter]

12:00.219 --> 12:02.922
Harvey, as a friend,

12:02.988 --> 12:04.690
{\an3}you have
very poor eyesight.

12:04.757 --> 12:06.358
(Technobear and Rooter)
Oh!

12:06.425 --> 12:07.660
We got an argument over here.

12:07.726 --> 12:10.296
Two friends disagreeing,
right over here.

12:10.362 --> 12:12.398
[excited chatter]

12:12.465 --> 12:15.067
Oh, no, what's happening?

12:15.134 --> 12:18.437
Kratz just dissed you, Harvey,
making you look like a fool.

12:18.504 --> 12:20.539
{\an1}Oh, guys,
we were just talking

12:20.606 --> 12:22.341
{\an1}about that cloud
that looks like a horse.

12:22.408 --> 12:24.143
It looks like a face.

12:24.210 --> 12:26.078
{\an1}You two friends
having a little argument,

12:26.145 --> 12:27.046
{\an3}so we're gonna help you
get through it.

12:27.113 --> 12:29.482
{\an3}So, that way,
you'll stay friends.

12:29.548 --> 12:31.450
Uh, how do we do that?

12:31.517 --> 12:33.319
(both)
You guys got to fight.

12:33.385 --> 12:36.288
[dramatic music]

12:36.355 --> 12:43.295
♪ ♪

12:43.362 --> 12:44.497
What? No!

12:44.563 --> 12:45.798
Kratz is my friend.

12:45.865 --> 12:46.465
I don't want to fight him.

12:46.532 --> 12:47.233
We're friends?

12:47.299 --> 12:49.034
{\an3}Yeah, dude.

12:49.101 --> 12:50.069
We hang out all the time.

12:50.136 --> 12:51.670
{\an3}We're hanging out
right now.

12:51.737 --> 12:53.639
{\an1}And if you guys
want to stay friends,

12:53.706 --> 12:55.608
{\an1}you got to punch him
until he agrees with you.

12:55.674 --> 12:57.910
{\an1}Or he punches you
until you agree with him.

12:57.977 --> 12:58.677
You guys punch each other.

12:58.744 --> 12:59.578
That's the main thing.

12:59.645 --> 13:01.647
That doesn't sound right.

13:01.714 --> 13:02.681
We're just having
a disagreement.

13:02.748 --> 13:04.850
I don't want
to fight about it.

13:04.917 --> 13:06.051
{\an3}Yeah, no,
for real, though,

13:06.118 --> 13:07.153
{\an3}it's the only way
guys can solve disputes.

13:07.219 --> 13:09.188
{\an3}Absolutely.

13:09.255 --> 13:11.857
{\an3}The only language
guys understand is punches.

13:11.924 --> 13:13.259
What?
Who told you that?

13:13.325 --> 13:15.528
(both)
My dad.

13:15.594 --> 13:16.562
{\an3}Oh.

13:16.629 --> 13:17.630
Well, I'm a guy.

13:17.696 --> 13:18.631
You're a guy.

13:18.697 --> 13:19.431
Yeah, I'm a guy.

13:19.498 --> 13:21.367
Guess we should fight.

13:21.433 --> 13:22.368
{\an1}Okay.

13:22.434 --> 13:24.036
[both grunting]

13:24.103 --> 13:26.272
{\an1}[sighs]

13:26.338 --> 13:28.107
{\an1}We're gonna have to teach
you guys how to fight.

13:28.174 --> 13:30.342
Yeah, all right.
I'll take Kratz.

13:30.409 --> 13:31.277
Technobear will take Harvey.

13:31.343 --> 13:32.845
We'll meet back
at noon tomorrow

13:32.912 --> 13:34.246
at Snapdragon Meadows.

13:34.313 --> 13:36.482
{\an3}It'll be the brawl
of the century.

13:36.549 --> 13:39.218
Okay, buddy,
let's have the best fight ever.

13:39.285 --> 13:41.353
Okay.

13:41.420 --> 13:43.923
[snoring]

13:43.989 --> 13:45.090
Listen up, Kratz.

13:45.157 --> 13:46.692
{\an3}We both know
you're too weak and scrawny

13:46.759 --> 13:48.260
{\an3}to win a fight
on your own.

13:48.327 --> 13:48.961
Agreed.

13:49.028 --> 13:50.796
But I've got a plan.

13:50.863 --> 13:52.064
You're gonna use your face
to intimidate Harvey.

13:52.131 --> 13:54.466
It'll be easier to punch him
when he's scared.

13:54.533 --> 13:56.402
Show me what you got.

13:56.468 --> 13:57.369
{\an3}Scare me.

13:57.436 --> 13:59.071
Uh...

13:59.138 --> 14:01.307
Blegh.

14:01.373 --> 14:02.608
Hey, that's it.

14:02.675 --> 14:03.576
{\an3}That's what
I'm talking about.

14:03.642 --> 14:04.577
Yes.

14:04.643 --> 14:05.544
Okay, then.

14:05.611 --> 14:07.179
Let's try showing some teeth.

14:07.246 --> 14:08.547
Argh!

14:08.614 --> 14:09.281
Arr.

14:09.348 --> 14:11.183
Yeah, that's it.

14:11.250 --> 14:12.051
Your face is gonna
send him running.

14:12.117 --> 14:14.620
{\an3}Now add
some primal screams.

14:14.687 --> 14:15.955
[screaming]

14:16.021 --> 14:18.324
[screaming weakly]

14:18.390 --> 14:18.891
One more more time.

14:18.958 --> 14:20.426
[screaming]

14:20.492 --> 14:21.760
[screams weakly]

14:21.827 --> 14:23.963
[both screaming]

14:26.031 --> 14:28.133
{\an3}All right, man,
you ready to train?

14:28.200 --> 14:29.101
Totally.

14:29.168 --> 14:31.136
I already did
all my stretches.

14:31.203 --> 14:32.338
You're gonna have to forget

14:32.404 --> 14:34.506
everything you think
you know about fighting.

14:34.573 --> 14:35.307
[bell dings]

14:35.374 --> 14:38.410
[crowd cheering]

14:38.477 --> 14:39.578
Done.

14:39.645 --> 14:40.980
All right, let's set the mood.

14:41.046 --> 14:42.982
[upbeat techno music]
- Yeah.

14:43.048 --> 14:46.352
{\an3}Just, like,
feel the rhythm for a bit.

14:46.418 --> 14:48.387
Start to groove with it.

14:48.454 --> 14:50.356
{\an3}Now, like pretty much
everything in life,

14:50.422 --> 14:52.258
{\an3}fighting is just like
being in the club.

14:52.324 --> 14:53.392
So check it out.

14:53.459 --> 14:55.361
{\an3}Imagine the DJ
won't play your record.

14:55.427 --> 14:57.663
{\an3}So you're like,
"Yo, play my record.

14:57.730 --> 14:58.764
Play my record."

14:58.831 --> 14:59.765
Play my record.

14:59.832 --> 15:00.966
{\an3}Good.

15:01.033 --> 15:02.901
Then the DJ puts on
your favorite jam,

15:02.968 --> 15:04.069
so you're feeling it.

15:04.136 --> 15:05.170
{\an3}So you're like,
"Bam, bam!"

15:05.237 --> 15:07.306
{\an1}Bam, bam!

15:07.373 --> 15:09.074
{\an3}Okay, now somebody's
trying to get you

15:09.141 --> 15:11.510
{\an3}to stop dancing so hard
next to their girlfriend,

15:11.577 --> 15:13.712
so you're all like, "No."

15:13.779 --> 15:14.680
{\an1}No!

15:14.747 --> 15:17.082
♪ ♪

15:17.149 --> 15:18.651
{\an3}Let's throw in
a new move here.

15:18.717 --> 15:20.152
Your mom walks in the room.

15:20.219 --> 15:22.755
{\an3}She's like, "I'm tired
of hearing your dumb music.

15:22.821 --> 15:23.756
Turn it down!"

15:23.822 --> 15:24.757
So you're like,

15:24.823 --> 15:25.924
{\an3}"No, Ma,
this music is who I am.

15:25.991 --> 15:28.627
"Fine, I will go live
outside, Ma.

15:28.694 --> 15:29.595
"How about that?

15:29.662 --> 15:30.763
Good-bye forever!"

15:30.829 --> 15:32.364
{\an3}[panting]

15:32.431 --> 15:33.565
{\an3}Okay, whew.

15:33.632 --> 15:35.267
Let's take a 30.

15:35.334 --> 15:36.969
{\an3}[slurping]

15:37.036 --> 15:38.470
{\an1}You're doing great,
Harvey.

15:38.537 --> 15:39.505
{\an3}Thanks.

15:39.571 --> 15:40.572
Did you see me, Fee?

15:40.639 --> 15:41.607
I think I'm ready.

15:41.674 --> 15:42.841
{\an1}What? No.

15:42.908 --> 15:44.643
{\an1}Harvey, you shouldn't
be fighting.

15:44.710 --> 15:45.778
Wait, why?

15:45.844 --> 15:47.146
I thought
you were all about fighting.

15:47.212 --> 15:48.580
Not for you.
You're gonna get killed.

15:48.647 --> 15:51.383
No, I've got skills now.

15:51.450 --> 15:53.118
{\an8}Change the record,
change the re--

15:53.185 --> 15:54.420
{\an1}Stop.

15:54.486 --> 15:55.754
No matter how many moves
you learn from a dancing bear,

15:55.821 --> 15:58.190
you're too nice to ever fight,

15:58.257 --> 16:00.159
and something bad's gonna happen
if you try.

16:00.225 --> 16:02.861
{\an3}You have to trust me.
I can handle this.

16:02.928 --> 16:05.197
{\an1}All right, I tried.
Come on, Foo.

16:05.264 --> 16:05.898
We have to go find
a new best friend

16:05.964 --> 16:07.733
for after Harvey dies.

16:07.800 --> 16:09.201
Your dancing
was really pretty.

16:09.268 --> 16:11.170
{\an3}Okay, see you guys
at the fight.

16:11.236 --> 16:14.273
Honey, I just brought you
some lemonade.

16:14.340 --> 16:15.708
Harvey, what are you doing?

16:15.774 --> 16:16.408
Learning how to fight.

16:16.475 --> 16:18.377
[techno music]

16:18.444 --> 16:20.479
Oh, no.

16:20.546 --> 16:22.047
Oh, hey, Mrs. Beaks.

16:22.114 --> 16:23.849
I'm just teaching Harvey
a couple moves

16:23.916 --> 16:25.184
tos protect himself.

16:25.250 --> 16:26.785
But hey, how's abouts

16:26.852 --> 16:28.854
{\an1}I teach you some moves
of my own?

16:28.921 --> 16:30.122
A-wink-wink.

16:30.189 --> 16:32.057
{\an3}Yeah, okay, sweetie,
no, thank you.

16:32.124 --> 16:33.192
Now, why don't you
go wait over there?

16:33.258 --> 16:35.394
Ow!

16:35.461 --> 16:36.895
{\an3}Harvey Beaks,
now you listen to me.

16:36.962 --> 16:40.265
{\an3}You're never gonna
survive a fight.

16:40.332 --> 16:41.333
Why does everyone
keep saying that?

16:41.400 --> 16:44.603
Not unless you learn
how to fight dirty.

16:44.670 --> 16:45.738
Fight dirty?

16:45.804 --> 16:46.505
Fight dirty.

16:46.572 --> 16:48.607
Like, with mud?

16:48.674 --> 16:49.608
No.

16:49.675 --> 16:50.576
Oh.

16:50.642 --> 16:51.510
Okay, honey.

16:51.577 --> 16:53.779
Fighting dirty
is real simple.

16:53.846 --> 16:55.981
Step one:
get a carton of milk.

16:56.048 --> 16:58.417
Step two:
throw it in the face.

16:58.484 --> 17:01.220
Step three: give 'em
the ol' punch in the nose.

17:01.286 --> 17:02.121
Ha!

17:02.187 --> 17:03.722
And now you've won
the fight.

17:03.789 --> 17:05.891
Yeah, show that tree
who's boss.

17:05.958 --> 17:08.394
{\an3}Okay, now I want you
to try it on me.

17:08.460 --> 17:09.060
Are you sure?

17:09.127 --> 17:10.496
Trust me, sweetie.

17:10.561 --> 17:12.798
I've been in plenty
of street fights.

17:12.865 --> 17:15.467
Um, okay, then.

17:15.534 --> 17:17.836
Here I go.

17:17.903 --> 17:18.369
Throw!

17:18.436 --> 17:20.506
Ah!

17:20.571 --> 17:21.640
- Ow.
- Whoa!

17:21.707 --> 17:23.909
Boy, I like making chili.

17:23.976 --> 17:25.511
No!

17:25.577 --> 17:27.546
Punch!

17:27.613 --> 17:28.647
[gasps]

17:28.714 --> 17:29.848
[all groan]

17:29.915 --> 17:30.849
{\an3}Why?

17:30.916 --> 17:31.850
No.

17:31.917 --> 17:33.552
What have I done?

17:33.619 --> 17:37.423
I'm a monster!

17:38.457 --> 17:39.558
Hey, honey.

17:39.625 --> 17:41.460
Don't worry
about what happened today.

17:41.527 --> 17:44.963
Just try and get some sleep
for tomorrow, okay?

17:45.030 --> 17:46.031
How can I sleep?

17:46.098 --> 17:49.067
If I fight Kratz
with these fists,

17:49.134 --> 17:50.636
I'm gonna kill him.

17:50.702 --> 17:51.904
[sighs]

17:51.970 --> 17:55.207
I just want to keep
being friends with my friend.

17:55.274 --> 17:56.975
I don't want to hurt him.

17:57.042 --> 18:00.612
- It's okay, Harvey.
- Who said that?

18:00.679 --> 18:02.481
- Down here.
- What?

18:02.548 --> 18:05.717
{\an3}Harvey, we were built
for destruction.

18:05.784 --> 18:08.987
No, you were built
for clapping and handshakes.

18:09.054 --> 18:11.757
You don't control us anymore.

18:11.824 --> 18:13.325
{\an1}I'm not gonna let you
hurt people.

18:13.392 --> 18:16.562
We're gonna hurt Kratz tomorrow
and then...

18:16.628 --> 18:19.298
destroy the world!

18:19.364 --> 18:22.067
No!

18:23.435 --> 18:25.471
[gasps]

18:25.537 --> 18:27.272
[sighs]

18:27.339 --> 18:29.842
Man, I don't know
what to do.

18:32.244 --> 18:33.846
(Technobear)
All right, Snapdragon Meadow,

18:33.912 --> 18:35.514
make some noise!

18:35.581 --> 18:37.950
This is the championship fight
to determine

18:38.016 --> 18:39.785
whether that one cloud
looks like a horse

18:39.852 --> 18:42.187
or some kind of
screaming monster or whatever.

18:42.254 --> 18:43.422
I think it looks like
a raspberry.

18:43.489 --> 18:45.324
Ooh!

18:45.390 --> 18:47.659
{\an3}After this knockdown,
drag-out battle,

18:47.726 --> 18:50.329
{\an3}the fighters will go back
to being very good friends.

18:50.395 --> 18:52.097
{\an1}I don't want
to hurt anybody.

18:52.164 --> 18:54.600
It doesn't matter
what you want, Harvey.

18:54.666 --> 18:56.168
We're gonna punch Kratz.

18:56.235 --> 18:58.136
And you're gonna watch.

18:58.203 --> 19:00.405
I hate you, murder-fists.

19:00.472 --> 19:04.776
Weighing in at 22 pounds of head
and 8 pounds of everything else,

19:04.843 --> 19:07.045
Harvey Beaks!

19:07.112 --> 19:08.847
[Harvey grunting]

19:10.716 --> 19:12.050
Hey, tough guy,

19:12.117 --> 19:12.718
{\an3}feeling good
about the fight?

19:12.784 --> 19:14.486
- No.
- Great.

19:14.553 --> 19:16.788
{\an3}Nice.

19:16.855 --> 19:18.524
{\an3}If you two are done
with your fashion show,

19:18.590 --> 19:21.159
{\an3}it's time to introduce
a real warrior.

19:21.226 --> 19:25.197
Behold Kratz the Killer!

19:28.100 --> 19:29.501
Oi, do the thing.

19:29.568 --> 19:30.602
Oh, right.

19:30.669 --> 19:33.906
[screams weakly]

19:33.972 --> 19:35.173
That's pretty good.

19:35.240 --> 19:35.908
Yeah, you got him scared.

19:35.974 --> 19:37.976
Now finish him off.

19:38.043 --> 19:39.611
Okay.

19:39.678 --> 19:41.480
[grunting]

19:41.547 --> 19:42.314
[cheering]

19:42.381 --> 19:43.916
Okay, Harvey,
it's go time.

19:43.982 --> 19:45.751
Now mess this dude up!

19:45.817 --> 19:48.186
[cheering]

19:48.253 --> 19:49.788
[camera shutter clicks]

19:49.855 --> 19:52.824
[cheering continues]

19:55.460 --> 19:56.895
{\an3}(left fist)
This is it, Harvey.

19:56.962 --> 19:59.831
{\an5}(right fist)
We're gonna pound Kratz
into paste.

19:59.898 --> 20:03.869
[fists laughing]

20:03.936 --> 20:05.737
No.

20:05.804 --> 20:07.773
I refuse to fight!

20:07.839 --> 20:09.308
[all gasp]

20:09.374 --> 20:10.475
- Wait, what?
- What?

20:10.542 --> 20:11.977
- They can do that?
- Why would you do that?

20:12.044 --> 20:13.745
{\an1}I'm sorry, Kratz,
but I won't do this.

20:13.812 --> 20:16.481
{\an1}I'm not gonna let
my murder-fists hurt you.

20:16.548 --> 20:19.851
{\an3}We can't be friends anymore
if we don't punch each other.

20:19.918 --> 20:20.819
Come on, guys.

20:20.886 --> 20:21.420
Somebody has to get punched.

20:21.486 --> 20:23.221
Ow!

20:23.288 --> 20:24.089
(fists)
He's right.

20:24.156 --> 20:26.191
Somebody has to get punched.

20:26.258 --> 20:29.528
Well, then I know
what I have to do.

20:31.630 --> 20:32.564
Ugh!

20:32.631 --> 20:33.565
What?

20:33.632 --> 20:34.566
Ugh!

20:34.633 --> 20:35.534
{\an1}What?

20:35.601 --> 20:38.170
[grunting]

20:38.236 --> 20:40.305
Harvey,
what are you doing?

20:40.372 --> 20:42.441
Yeah, Harvey,
what's with the crazy stuff?

20:42.507 --> 20:44.977
I don't want
to fight my friends.

20:45.043 --> 20:46.578
I want to help them.

20:46.645 --> 20:48.847
So if you want
to beat up Harvey,

20:48.914 --> 20:49.581
I'll help beat up Harvey.

20:49.648 --> 20:51.516
Ugh!

20:51.583 --> 20:52.784
{\an3}Kratz,
now's your chance.

20:52.851 --> 20:53.952
Go beat him up.

20:54.019 --> 20:55.587
[whimpering]

20:55.654 --> 20:57.456
Ugh!

20:57.522 --> 20:58.657
{\an3}Wait, wait,
why is he doing it now?

20:58.724 --> 21:00.692
Kratz?

21:00.759 --> 21:01.727
I don't know.

21:01.793 --> 21:02.461
It just felt right.

21:02.527 --> 21:03.996
I didn't teach him this.

21:04.062 --> 21:05.030
Did you teach him this?

21:05.097 --> 21:06.365
{\an3}No, I didn't
teach him this.

21:06.431 --> 21:07.165
- Guys, what are you doing?
- What's going on?

21:07.232 --> 21:10.068
We're solving an argument.

21:10.135 --> 21:11.169
[grunts]

21:11.236 --> 21:12.671
Boy, this got weird real quick.

21:12.738 --> 21:16.408
[both grunting]

21:16.475 --> 21:17.809
So are we friends now?

21:17.876 --> 21:20.712
We were always friends.

21:20.779 --> 21:22.581
Cool, Kratz.

21:22.648 --> 21:24.483
[both grunt]

21:27.185 --> 21:30.856
{\an1}What is it
with boys and fighting?

21:30.922 --> 21:32.224
I don't know.

21:32.290 --> 21:33.659
{\an3}They're, like,
all so terrible at it.

21:33.725 --> 21:35.293
Why even try?

21:35.360 --> 21:37.129
Well, it's done wonders
for our relationship.

21:37.195 --> 21:38.163
I love you, man.

21:38.230 --> 21:40.432
I love you so much!

21:40.499 --> 21:43.168
{\an3}It's beautiful,
Harvey.

21:43.235 --> 21:45.370
It sure is, Kratz.

21:50.375 --> 21:54.246
A wonderful lesson
in friendship has been learned.

21:54.312 --> 21:55.480
Treat your friends

21:55.547 --> 21:59.885
as the magnificent diamonds
that they are.

21:59.951 --> 22:03.722
Have a good night.

22:03.789 --> 22:05.724
[cheerful music]

22:05.791 --> 22:14.533
♪ ♪
